		<div id="comment_body_64732778"><p>The formal reasons for the arrest are, on the face of it, a part of the ridiculous and bullshit drive to destroy privacy of communication in Europe, unsurprisingly lead by the French version of Stasi. OMG, think of the children.</p><p>That line of attack is not an attack on Durov or Kremlin or whatever, it is an attack on the European citizens.</p><p>I'll refrain from speculating what real reasons are there for the arrest, as there is too little to speculate on. For some reason, though, Whatsapp's owners aren't persecute<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64732778">

